| Layer              | AWS Service                   | Purpose                        |
| ------------------ | ----------------------------- | ------------------------------ |
| Compute            | **AWS Lambda**                | Serverless function runtime    |
| API Gateway        | **Amazon API Gateway**        | REST API entry point           |
| Database           | **DynamoDB**                  | NoSQL data storage per service |
| Messaging          | **Amazon SQS / SNS**          | Service communication          |
| Storage (optional) | **Amazon S3**                 | File uploads or static content |
| Identity/Auth      | **Amazon Cognito / IAM**      | Secure user auth               |
| Monitoring         | **CloudWatch, X-Ray**         | Logs, metrics, tracing         |
| IaC                | **Terraform / AWS SAM / CDK** | Infrastructure as Code         |
